{"tid":2058630,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想問本田freed","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T00:37:49.000Z","uid":52173,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd365574512cf6f584db877ef15eba84a2a9613","tid":2058630,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴打對本田freed 大約10-12萬budget <br />\n平均一日行100km <br />\nHighway 60%-70% 市區30-40%<br />\n連司機加乘客3-4個人<br />\n電油版同油電版 大約$？/km<br />\n宜家部車好似$1.5-1.6/km<br />\n值唔值得換呢部車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b7bf83648b81671a5e19414ce670aebd9b9b32","tid":2058630,"uid":277374,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7cd365574512cf6f584db877ef15eba84a2a9613","tid":2058630,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴打對本田freed 大約10-12萬budget <br />\n平均一日行100km <br />\nHighway 60%-70% 市區30-40%<br />\n連司機加乘客3-4個人<br />\n電油版同油電版 大約$？/km<br />\n宜家部車好似$1.5-1.6/km<br />\n值唔值得換呢部車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"鍾意咪值，唔鍾意咪唔值，點答好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n油錢差一角幾毫咁重要咩？我覺得香港揸車應該係睇你有幾意揸車，幾鍾意部車同埋整體有幾滿意 (例如一家大細出去玩，有人可能為咗媾女，或者返放工慳一半時間等等)"},{"pid":"dd637f87a65bdb3a08039a681e7fe683a4c3cd97","tid":2058630,"uid":119199,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"當佢 $1/km<br />\n<br />\n你一個月慳到 $900，一年慳到 $10800 油錢<br />\n但你換一換車就唔止洗多一萬蚊<br />\n<br />\n結論：慳唔到好多錢，隨自己喜歡啦<br />\n<br />\n不過 Freed 我坐過幾次，睇車都睇過兩架<br />\n空間感一般，頭頂有點壓迫感"},{"pid":"a90527737f7371e1bd45283fa3cfada8ca36df12","tid":2058630,"uid":60109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"用唔著咁大部我寧願jazz"},{"pid":"34301e795c007a334632ab17e6604ab2776c725b","tid":2058630,"uid":277374,"like"